WEBVTT

00:01:58.564 --> 00:02:00.863
If you're happy and you know it,
clap your hands.

00:02:00.887 --> 00:02:01.980
(Claps)

00:02:02.004 --> 00:02:04.523
Now you're talking!

00:02:04.547 --> 00:02:07.114
(In Spanish: For all the people 
who speak Spanish,

00:02:07.144 --> 00:02:08.938
please stand up.

00:02:10.575 --> 00:02:14.244
And look at a person sitting to your side

00:02:14.268 --> 00:02:16.205
and start laughing.)

00:02:16.229 --> 00:02:19.552
(Laughter)

00:02:19.552 --> 00:02:21.703
Thank you so much.
Please be seated.

00:02:21.727 --> 00:02:23.825
Now, if that felt a little bit awkward,

00:02:23.849 --> 00:02:27.466
I promise there was no joke
being had at your expense.

00:02:27.490 --> 00:02:31.773
I simply asked the Spanish-speaking
audience to stand up,